@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ - Help Center";
}

<section class="faq-header py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 text-primary fw-bold f-calvino">
            Help Center
        </h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted mb-5 f-calvino">
            Get help with your reservations, account, and more.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-info py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-4">
            <h2 class="display-6 text-primary fw-bold f-calvino">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="text-muted f-calvino">
                We're here to help you! Feel free to reach out with any questions.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 text-center">
                <h5 class="fw-bold">Phone</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    <strong>
                        <a href="tel:+905300907998" class="text-muted text-decoration-none">0530 090 79 98</a>
                    </strong>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 text-center">
                <h5 class="fw-bold">Email</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">
                    <strong>
                        <a href="mailto:info@sailingandpeople.com"
                            class="text-muted text-decoration-none">info@sailingandpeople.com</a>
                    </strong>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="faq-section py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="display-6 text-primary fw-bold f-calvino">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeading1">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#faqCollapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faqCollapse1">
                        Do I need any qualifications or documents to sail?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqCollapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faqHeading1"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        You do not need any documents or qualifications for crewed boat rentals. When the boat is
                        sailing, you can either sit and enjoy the sailing or you can assist with the information given
                        by the captain.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeading2">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#faqCollapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse2">
                        Which rental type is most suitable for us?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqCollapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading2"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        In Private Yacht Rental; All details such as boat selection, tour date, food menu, and tour
                        program are determined according to your wishes. Our experienced staff provides special service
                        just for you and your group's satisfaction.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeading3">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#faqCollapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse3">
                        Can we visit the Greek Islands?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqCollapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading3"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        As Siesta Yachting, we can prepare tour programs for you covering one or more Greek Islands.
                        Additional taxes to be paid for Greek waters, marina/port fees on the islands, and other
                        expenses are not included in the price.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeading4">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#faqCollapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse4">
                        What is included in the rental fee?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqCollapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading4"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        In gulets and sailboats; Port fees in Turkish territorial waters, port taxes, yacht insurance,
                        cleaning of boat laundry, potable water, bottled gas, and transitlog are included in the price.
                        Also in gulets; Fuel and personnel service are also included in the price.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faqHeading5">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                        data-bs-target="#faqCollapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqCollapse5">
                        Is smoking allowed on the boat?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqCollapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faqHeading5"
                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Smoking is not allowed in the saloon and cabins for health and safety reasons. Passengers who
                        smoke can smoke on deck.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="additional-info py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
                <p class="text-muted">
                    If you have more questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact us.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
